name: H2O
public_notice: The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: H2O is an OCEAN backed stable asset native to the Web3 data economy. H2O is based on the RAI stable asset by Reflexer Labs. Like RAI, H2O is decentralized, permissionless, minimizes governance and carries great potential for data marketplaces. The asset will serve as the medium of exchange in the Ocean Protocol ecosystem in addition to the native $OCEAN token.
